dataset.name: Hyundai Mipo Dockyard Co., Ltd. (010620)
dataset.description: HYUNDAI MIPO DOCKYARD.CO.,LTD. is a Korea-based company principally engaged in the shipbuilding business. The Company operates in two business divisions: shipbuilding and financial. Its shipbuilding division involves in the construction of a wide array of vessels, including medium-sized product carriers, chemical tankers, cable and pipe laying vessels, bulk carriers, container ships, drill ships, petroleum carriers (PCs), pure car truck carriers (PCTCs) and floating production storage and offloading (FPSO) ships, liquefied petroleum gas (LPG) carriers, as well as platform supply vessels (PSVs), among others. Its financial division involves in the provision of asset management services, initial public offerings (IPO), mergers and acquisitions (M&A) consulting and other financial services.
